{"GENIAL":[{"def":"Contributing to, or concerned in, propagation or production; generative; procreative; productive.","pos":""},{"def":"Contributing to, and sympathizing with, the enjoyment of life; sympathetically cheerful and cheering; jovial and inspiring joy or happiness; exciting pleasure and sympathy; enlivening; kindly; as, she was of a cheerful and genial disposition.","pos":""}],"GENIALITY":[{"def":"The quality of being genial; sympathetic cheerfulness; warmth of disposition and manners.","pos":""}],"GENIALLY":[{"def":"By genius or nature; naturally.","pos":""},{"def":"Gayly; cheerfully.","pos":""}],"GENIALNESS":[{"def":"The quality of being genial.","pos":""}],"GENIAN":[{"def":"Of or pertaining to the chin; mental; as, the genian prominence.","pos":""}],"GENICULATE":[{"def":"Bent abruptly at an angle, like the knee when bent; as, a geniculate stem; a geniculate ganglion; a geniculate twin crystal.","pos":""}],"GENICULATED":[{"def":"Same as Geniculate.","pos":""}],"GENICULATION":[{"def":"The act of kneeling.","pos":""},{"def":"The state of being bent abruptly at an angle.","pos":""}],"GENIO":[{"def":"A man of a particular turn of mind.","pos":""}],"GENIOHYOID":[{"def":"Of or pertaining to the chin and hyoid bone; as, the geniohyoid muscle.","pos":""}],"GENIPAP":[{"def":"The edible fruit of a West Indian tree (Genipa Americana) of the order Rubiaceæ.","pos":""}],"GENISTA":[{"def":"A genus of plants including the common broom of Western Europe.","pos":""}],"GENITAL":[{"def":"Pertaining to generation, or to the generative organs.","pos":""}],"GENITALS":[{"def":"The organs of generation; the sexual organs; the private parts.","pos":""}],"GENITING":[{"def":"A species of apple that ripens very early.","pos":""}],"GENITIVAL":[{"def":"Possessing genitive from; pertaining to, or derived from, the genitive case; as, a genitival adverb.","pos":""}],"GENITIVE":[{"def":"Of or pertaining to that case (as the second case of Latin and Greek nouns) which expresses source or possession.","pos":""}],"GENITOCRURAL":[{"def":"Pertaining to the genital organs and the thigh; -- applied especially to one of the lumbar nerves.","pos":""}],"GENITOR":[{"def":"One who begets; a generator; an originator.","pos":""}],"GENITOURINARY":[{"def":"Gen`i*to*u\"ri*na*ry, a.","pos":""}],"GENITURE":[{"def":"Generation; procreation; birth.","pos":""}],"GENIUS":[{"def":"A good or evil spirit, or demon, supposed by the ancients to preside over a man's destiny in life; a tutelary deity; a supernatural being; a spirit, good or bad.","pos":""}]}